about.summary: A chain-able generator for python; inspired by the syntactical sugar of java stream

name: pystreamer
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyStreamer" %}
{% set version = "0.1.2" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e9ff94c97517a686d41e58fa163e543a340bf802b9c5a911aa7c4833c05c29e4
  
build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - streamer

about:
  home: https://github.com/Arnoldosmium/pystreamer
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A chain-able generator for python; inspired by the syntactical sugar of java stream'
  dev_url: https://github.com/Arnoldosmium/pystreamer

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Arnoldosmium
